From 29939eb4c40db3b2d82e20cbad9a67c7da148eeb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Thu, 21 May 2026 07:38:54 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 10/84] Anchor native popup windows

A hidden window learned the map,
And shuffled to the pane;
The popups found the neighborhood,
Though y still needs a lane.
